# Chicken Adobo

The combination of chicken, soy sauce, vinegar, garlic, and fried potato chunks creates a bold and savory taste that is hard to resist.

## Ingredients

- Chicken pieces
- Soy sauce
- Vinegar
- Garlic
- Potatoes
- Black peppercorns
- Bay leaves
